dc_description_s: 1 map ; 36 x 48 cm.|Relief shown pictorially.|North is oriented to the left.|Illustrations include a dog, compass, and coat of arms around the scale cartouche and fruit around the title cartouche.|This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson between 1631 and 1633.|From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
